{"tid":2448330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中印角力］SOHO中國潘石屹子疑詆毀英烈遭跨境追捕","createTime":"2021-03-16T00:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T11:26:38.000Z","uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c725d06584197caed188c32815df994924ee9f6","tid":2448330,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:12:51.000Z","msg":"內地官方對「侮辱戍邊士兵言論」的紅線，越拉越闊、越拉越嚴，連超級富二代也不能倖免。大地產商「SOHO中國」創辦人潘石屹之子、目前身處海外的潘瑞，疑於去年6月中印爆發衝突時，發佈「侮辱戍邊士兵言論」，傳被北京市海淀公安分局決定對其採取依法刑事拘留，並對他展開追捕，敦促其盡快回國「接受調查」。有學者向《蘋果》表示，連串事件顯示官方有意利用領土問題推高民族主義情緒，批評內地不是以事實澄清質疑，而是高壓噤聲，更或動輒禍及家人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210316/QENL6RYM2RBTXPCB25Y3HOOBXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210316%2FQENL6RYM2RBTXPCB25Y3HOOBXQ%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=45665322\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210316%2FQENL6RYM2RBTXPCB25Y3HOOBXQ%2F&h=8f0a62aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210316/QENL6RYM2RBTXPCB25Y3HOOBXQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n中印角力丨SOHO中國潘石屹子疑詆毀英烈遭跨境追捕 學者：官方有意鼓動民族情緒"},{"pid":"38b0203a172f196cbfa5a4720d19d08ec016d242","tid":2448330,"uid":58209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:16:07.000Z","msg":"中国护照也许不能让你去世界的任何一个地方，但是只要你手持中国护照，祖国就可以把你接回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb56ceeaa73da04df67e9d53d1c1e0ac696be5a","tid":2448330,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"38b0203a172f196cbfa5a4720d19d08ec016d242","tid":2448330,"uid":58209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:16:07.000Z","msg":"中国护照也许不能让你去世界的任何一个地方，但是只要你手持中国护照，祖国就可以把你接回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:17:43.000Z","msg":"潘石屹又唔知要使幾多錢擺平"},{"pid":"d9a0c0757673934331e3c1a5aebdc8d8ef3f360e","tid":2448330,"uid":51271,"like":0,"d